overview: The 2023 Spring Breakin' was the second annual Spring Breakin' professional wrestling event produced by WWE. It was held primarily for wrestlers from the NXT brand division. Spring Breakin' aired as a special episode of NXT. The television special took place on April 25, 2023, at the WWE Performance Center in Orlando, Florida.
tagline: Trunk match: Tony D'Angelo, Lorenzo vs Pretty Deadly. Cora Jade vs Lyra Valkyria. World title: Carmelo vs Waller. Women's title: Indi Hartwell vs Roxanne Perez.
title: WWE NXT Spring Breakin' 2023
